<div class="row">
  <div class="grey col">
    <section class="col col-720">
      <p class="inset">
        Every day, people are being accepted onto teacher training courses starting this September. Places fill up quickly at this time of year so don’t miss your opportunity to join a course while there’s still time to apply.
      </p>
      
    </div>
    </section>

  <section class="col col-720">
    <h2 class="heading--box-blue">Get help to apply on time</h2>

    <div class="inset">
      <p>
        Our teacher training advisers can save you time on research and guide you through everything you need to know to apply for teacher training.
      </p>

      <p>They can help you with:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>creating a personal statement that shows off your strengths</li>
        <li>preparing for interviews</li>
      </ul>

      <p><%= link_to("Get a teacher training adviser", page_path("teacher-training-advisers")) %>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

    <section class="col col-720">
    <h2 class="heading--box-blue">Find a teacher training course</h2>
    <div class="inset">
      <p>
      Teacher training courses usually take 9 months full-time, or 18 to 24 months part-time.
      </p>
      <p>
      Most courses involve school placements with some theoretical learning.
      </p>
      <a href="https://www.gov.uk/find-postgraduate-teacher-training-courses">Find postgraduate teacher training</a>.
    </div>
  </section>

    <section class="col col-720">

    <h2 class="heading--box-blue">If you’re a non-UK citizen</h2>

    <div class="inset">
      <p>
        If you’re a non-UK citizen, the application process takes longer so not all providers will accept you onto a course at this stage.
      </p>
      <p>Learn more about <%= link_to("training to teach in England as a non-UK citizen", page_path("non-uk-teachers/train-to-teach-in-england-as-an-international-student")) %>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="col col-720">

    <h2 class="heading--box-blue">If you need more time</h2>

    <div class="inset">
      <p>
        Don’t worry if you’re not quite ready to apply yet. Applications will open in October for next year’s courses.
      </p>
      <p>To get a reminder nearer the time, as well as helpful tips and advice to get you one step closer to a career in teaching, <%= link_to("sign up for our emails", page_path("mailinglist/signup/name")) %>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
